                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>30 feet. A creature entering or starting its turn in the aura must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:27] save or become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (plus @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} as long as it's sickened on a critical failure). A holy creature takes a –2 status penalty to this saving throw. A creature that succeeds at its save or recovers from being sickened is temporarily immune to blasphemous stench for 1 minute unless it is holy.</p>"
