                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The first time each round that a living creature takes damage from a carrion angel's claw Strike, it must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:30|options:inflicts:drained,inflicts:sickened] save to avoid becoming @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1} on a failure (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2} on a critical failure).</p>"
